phrases: Far beyond the deep blue Earth, you and I shall meet...
A snow-white feather comes fluttering down, swaying gently in the air.
Without holding back, I want to envelope you, my one and only love.
I know I have the power to protect the one I love, right here in my hands.
Just as I have always dreamed.
Let the wind carry off your hopes, faraway.
I have wings nobody can see.
They will take us to where we can be free.
It is just hard for me to believe, you know?
A girl like you making breakfast for me...
Oh, never mind, it is nothing.
Yeah, I will be at the university.
I have got to be there first period today.
Would that be the place we visited the other day?
Would it be all right if I came along?
That is not what I meant...
I have been invited to a yacht party that day with my father.
I managed to get tickets for that concert you wanted to see!
This is to prove my sincerity to you!
Her dad's the CEO of some hotshot company, and she is so good-looking.
No one can compete with that!
No girl in this school stands a chance against Sayoko...
The other day, I promised to take you on a tour of the campus, did not I?
I had no idea there would be so many people around!
It is not that I mind being with Belldandy...
After all, she is a goddess.
I do not remember seeing her before.
I think I will make a pass at her!
She is daring to mount a challenge against me, eh?
I just do not know what to make of everyone around here.
Something might be about to happen to you, Keiichi!
If something happens, it will be to you.
We are just on a walk, and now this.
What is going to happen later?
Why are you asking for her address?
Why are you asking for her address?
We will send over the stuff you left at the dorm to your new place.
Does that mean they are shacking up together?
The question is, why would she go out with such a loser?
You better jump ship to someone who is actually worthy of you!
Do not break your parents' hearts!
What do they mean by'shacking up together'?
Oh, well, it is like when a guy and a girl live together...
Here on Earth, do parents grieve when a man and woman live together?
No, but living together kind of means you are involved in a lot of ways...
Involved in a lot of ways?
Hey, no, not in that way exactly, but...
Let us take you on a campus tour.
Let us take you on a campus tour.
I just remembered I have an errand for you.
I need you to bring me something from the club room.
Do not tell me this was caused by...
You mean that thing that reacts when something tries to separate us?
I hope it does not turn into a huge headache for us.
You will learn about many things here.
Except this is not really the class I am supposed to be taking right now...
No problem, I am in this class.
Well, the last thing we need is for the System Force to kick in again.
I am sorry, but would you mind moving?
But they never said anything about assigned seats...
I will move to that side.
If you give up your seat, then you will be admitting defeat.
And if you refuse, everyone will think you are a little bitch.
I have got you in a no-win situation!
In that case, let us do this.
She handled the situation without sullying her reputation with the guys...
Well, it seems we have a full house today!
I have not seen you here before.
She does not understand Japanese that well yet...
Well, she must be if everyone says so.
Let us get this class underway.
It should be a piece of cake, then.
I will never let you take the title of Campus Queen from me.
That cat is the master of our school.
Is she a friend of yours?
This is Belldandy, an exchange student.
I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
There is no time to lose!
Professor Osawa heard about Belldandy and he is investigating her.
You know, Professor Osawa, who is always competing with Kakuta!
He heard some rumor about Kakuta...
What are we going to do?
What are we going to do?
We are going to hack into the Student Affairs file server.
Just hurry up and log into the Student Affairs server!
The password's taped up right there, see?
Log In Failed A wrong password...
They frickin' changed it on us, did they?
You are going to get in through sheer willpower!
Man, that is not it either.
Whosoever stands in our way, I bid you, open the door for us now!
Provide us with the key that will open that door!
She really is an exchange student here?
I am going to keep digging until I find the truth!
He does not quit, does he?
Let us make the next move.
I feel so bad about all the trouble.
Why do not we just put an end to it?
Now that it is come to this, it is our duty to protect you!
I have a feeling it is more out of a sense of mischief than of duty.
Now then, they must be ready to expel that girl by now...
Was it all right to let them do that?
Was it all right to let them do that?
Ugh, who gives a damn anymore?
Who knew that girl had it in her to go this far?
In that case I will be happy to take you on in person!
Since my junior high and high school days, I have been called'the Queen'.
Why do not I show you how terrible my wrath can be?
Come to think of it, I wonder what is going on with Miss Mishima.
Sorry, but I am not into old-fogey stuff like that.
No, it is nothing important, really.
You were remembering something that made you sad.
Those who are well-acquainted with grief will be visited by much happiness.
Well now, I did not think I would find you here.
Professor Osawa was looking for you.
Professor Osawa was looking for you.
You would better go see him right away.
You would better go see him right away.
Then I will be right back.
I have something to talk to you about.
You do not have to worry about me.
I know it might seem a little strange to ask you this out of the blue, but...
Are you going out with her?
Not exactly going with her, but...
Are you going out with her?
So you are not seeing her, right?
No man has ever been able to resist this tactic before!
Sorry, but this is the girl I have decided to go out with.
I will humiliate her to the point where she can never show her face here again!
You see, I have sort of had my eye on you all this time...
I mean, you know how you are always tinkering with that bike of yours?
My father used to work in a factory, you see.
So you do not like me?
No, it is not that at all, but...
Of course, if you are any kind of man that is exactly what you would say!
I did not know anybody was down there.
I knew the System Force would kick in at some point...
I was hoping I would get the chance to talk to you.
How do you like our college?
There is such a mixture of various emotions.
And there is a sweet little cat, too!
I do not think you should do that...
How did it come to this?
Professor Osawa was actually taking a break.
Are you calling me a liar?
No, that is not what I meant.
Why do not you show your true colors?
I know you are in a snit because I made a pass at your guy!
I am sorry, I just do not get the drift of what you are saying...
Who in the world are you, anyway?
Coming to Nekomi Tech all of a sudden!
You may be a goddess, but I am a Queen!
I will win over that runt, and leave you to drown in your own tears!
Did I... did I do something to upset her?
Jeez, we had a long day, did not we?
Well, in that case, I guess it is all right.
I said get in the car!
The System Force only reacts when something tries to pull us apart...
I will go on ahead, all right?
But how do we know she will take me straight home...
Just get in the car, will you?
Uh, you really do not need to rush.
But the sun's about to set.
There is a beach with a beautiful view of the sunset.
Let us go for a drive.
There was no construction going on yesterday!
It is the System Force after all.
Never mind, I will take another route.
Let us just give it up and go home.
It looks like the sun's already set anyway.
But I want you to answer one question.
This is terrible, Keiichi's in danger...
I cannot get there in time!
Whatever it was that tried to separate us is gone!
Look, I know you are not really in love with me.
You probably do not remember this, but I got rejected once, awhile ago...
That is why I can tell you do not really mean what you are saying.
Not that it does not make me feel good, though!
So do you think you can put an end to this now?
I guess I kind of upset Miss Mishima.
Wait, I left my bike at school.
Not that it does not make me feel good, though!
I was so cruel when I rejected him.
How can he smile about it?
Who can that be at this hour?
We made too much dinner, so...
Why do not we all eat together?
Oh, I do not see why not.
The seniors would not leave without trying some of Belldandy's cooking.
Oh yeah, the Dean told me to give you this.
It is your student ID card.
It is your student ID card.
It means that now you are officially a Nekomi Tech student, just like me.
That girl's going to stick around'til we graduate?
Why is this happening to me?
One day when I woke up...
A day like any other... another one just beginning.
There you are, yawning... your face is still so sleepy.
Because each peaceful day we share is a miracle to me.
This is where my heart will always return...
There is only one thing I wish for.
I chase after the same dream, wherever it may go.
The love I feel for you gives me strength.
May tomorrow be as joyful as today...
When two people of the opposite sex live under the same roof...
That goes not only for men and women, but goddesses and human beings too.
Next episode: Ah! Living Under One Roof Together!
Oh, man, am I supposed to live in agony?
